    <p>
        The Interactive Whiteboard is an integrated solution, combining State-Of-The-Art hardware with leading edge software, 
        creating a powerful interactive teaching tool. The Interactive Whiteboard brings ideas, lessons & resources to life! 
        You are able to write and draw over projected images, annotate in color, cut & paste images, highlight and capture it 
